---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout lang="en" title="Cookie Policy" description="Information about the use of cookies on this website.">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Cookie policy</h1>

    <div class="content-section">
      <h2>What are cookies?</h2>
      <p>
        Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit our website.
        They help us provide a better user experience and improve the site.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
      <h2>Types of cookies we use</h2>

      <div class="cookie-type">
        <h3>Essential cookies</h3>
        <p>
          These cookies are required for the website to function. They enable basic features
          such as security, network management, and accessibility. They are activated automatically
          and cannot be disabled.
        </p>
        <p><strong>Retention:</strong> Session or up to 1 year</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cookie-type">
        <h3>Functional cookies</h3>
        <p>
          These cookies allow the website to offer enhanced functionality and personalisation,
          such as language or display preferences.
        </p>
        <p><strong>Retention:</strong> Up to 1 year</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cookie-type">
        <h3>Analytics cookies</h3>
        <p>
          These cookies help us understand how visitors use the website. Information is aggregated
          and used in anonymised form where possible.
        </p>
        <p><strong>Retention:</strong> Up to 2 years</p>
        <p><strong>Services:</strong> Google Analytics, Matomo (if enabled)</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cookie-type">
        <h3>Marketing cookies</h3>
        <p>
          These cookies are used to measure reach and relevance of communications, including via
          Meta/Facebook (e.g. for education and community programmes). They are loaded only after consent.
        </p>
        <p><strong>Retention:</strong> Up to 2 years</p>
        <p><strong>Services:</strong> Meta Pixel (if enabled)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
      <h2>Managing your cookie settings</h2>
      <p>
        You can change your cookie preferences at any time via the cookie settings link in the footer
        or the settings button in the cookie banner.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
  }

  h1 {
    color: #111827;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .content-section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .content-section h2 {
    color: #111827;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .content-section p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #374151;
  }

  .cookie-type {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: #f9fafb;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
  }

  .cookie-type h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #111827;
  }

  .cookie-type p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #4b5563;
  }

  .cookie-type p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>
